            <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
                <note>This edition is based on <ref type="mss" corresp="UppQ1524o"/> on fols 22r, 23r. Division into verses is indicated with ፤  or ፤፤
                    (a four-dot asterisk with over- and underlining).
                    The end of the poem is indicated with ። .</note>
                <ab>
                    <l n="1">ተጼውዎቱ፡ ለ<choice><sic>ስ</sic><corr resp="JK">ሰ</corr></choice>ብእ፡ እመ፡ 
                        ከመ፡ ጽዮን፡ ኮነ፡ ምህርካ፡ ጽኑእ፡ እም፡ ተመነነ፤፤</l>
                    <l n="2">እመ፡ ጽዮንሃ፡ እለ፡ ጼወው፡ 
                        ፍጡ<del rend="overUnderlined">ን</del><add rend="above">ነ</add>፡ እስመ፡ 
                        ኮ<choice><sic>ኦ</sic><corr resp="JK">ኑ</corr></choice>፡ ጺውዋነ፤፤</l>
                    <l n="3">ወብሩህ፡ ገ<choice><sic>ጸ</sic><corr resp="JK">ጾ</corr></choice>ሙ፡ መልብስ፡ ኀዘን፡ ተከድነ፤</l>
                    <l n="4">እስመ፡ ቅድመ፡ አብዝሖ፡ ፍስሐ፡ ያመጽእ፡ ኃዘነ፤</l><pb n="23r"/>
                    <l n="5">መኳንንተ፡ ሥርአት፡ ወህግ፡ ካህናቲ<del rend="strikethrough">፤</del><choice><sic>ሂ</sic><corr resp="JK">ሃ</corr></choice>፡ 
                        ለደብረ፡ ጽዮን፡ እምነ፤</l>
                    <l n="6">ለህዝለ፡ ፍና፡ ርህቅት፡ ከመ፡ ትኩኑ፡ ጸወነ፤</l>
                    <l n="7">አምጣ<choice><sic>ን</sic><corr resp="JK">ነ</corr></choice>፡ ኮንክሙ፡ 
                        ብርሃነ፡ ወምድረ፡ ከንአን፡ ይእቲ፡ ደብርነ፤</l>
                    <l n="8">ዘታውህዝ፡ ፍቅረ፡ ሰብእ፡ መዓረ፡ ወወይነ።</l>
                </ab>
            </div>
